reviews.review_text:
Love the main game, and it has a great story. I've always loved Spider-Man comics and movies.

But there is one thing;
Why are there enemies there just to ruin the experience. There is an enemy type that if you don't focus will ruin you're whole day just because F you. You have to sit there and dodge until the perfect dodge actually stuns him, then you have to kill him. Worst part is, THERE ARE 50 OTHER ENEMIES KILLING YOU. I just don't understand the reason to add something that ruins the experience, and I'm not sure I even like Spider-Man now because of it.
